To access Booking App user is need to Login using an username and password. For an unregistered user there is option to register by providing the following info: first name, last name, email, password . After registration an confirmation email is sent to provided email address. User is able to recover forgotten or reset password based on email address, an email with link to reset password will be sent on provided email of an registered user. In case someone try to reset password with an unregistered email address, an message will be displayed with a suggestion to create an account/register.
